This project uses shadcn/ui CLI command 

# Add components
bunx --bun shadcn@latest add [component]

# Initialize project
bunx --bun shadcn@latest init

# Options for init
#   -d, --defaults    use default values (new-york, zinc, css variables)
#   -f, --force      force overwrite components.json
#   -y, --yes        skip confirmation
#   -c, --cwd <dir>  working directory

# Options for add
#   -y, --yes         skip confirmation
#   -o, --overwrite   overwrite existing files
#   -c, --cwd <dir>   working directory
#   -a, --all         add all components
#   -p, --path <path> custom component path

# Icons
For icons, use React Icons (https://react-icons.github.io/react-icons/icons/tb/)
Preferred icon sets:
- Tabler Icons (tb): import { TbIconName } from "react-icons/tb"

Example:
import { TbBrandGithub } from "react-icons/tb"
